wiki.summary: "Sorry Not Sorry" is a song recorded by American singer Demi Lovato. They co-wrote the song with Sean Douglas, Trevor Brown, William Zaire Simmons and the producer Oak Felder. It was released on July 11, 2017, through Island Records, Republic, Hollywood Records, and Safehouse Records, as the lead single from their sixth studio album Tell Me You Love Me. Read more on Last.fm.
